You will note by my signature line that I am protesting the nerfing of our noble class, yet again.  What is it this time, you ask?<P>Gestapo Grouping Enforcement.  We now get more XP for being in a group.  If we do NOT group we dont get as much XP and we take a higher death penalty when we die.<P>Since the patch I have spent all my time non-leveling, LFG in many, many zones.  Today I was told I would be allowed in for evac purposes only since I was just a "low rent mage without a pet".  The guy was right.  Like level mages can now outnuke wizzies.<P>No play, no ports.  I am a lone voice, but I've reached others and they will reach more.  Together we will protest this and together we will get our class balanced.  This is a good example of "class balance":<P>Outraged Individual:  You cant port me to Cazic Thule!  It's instant death!  Just add water!<P>Balanced Wizzie:  Oh no!  If it were unsafe at this level Verant would not allow us to do something that unsafe... maybe you'd better ask a GM about it... I'm sure you're mistaken =)<P>------------------<BR>Severine Wolfe<BR>Not Porting to Anywhere
</FONT>
