Ok here we go <P>My view on the Wiz class is this.<P>1) Why is it that from 50 to 60 our best spells are still drought, Ice Comet and Tears all 54 &#8211; spells?<BR>2) Why at 55 with good gear cant I finish a mob in SF I run out of mana <BR>3) Why do we take a 60% hit on spells in Pvp but dots still hit for 80% Wiz has to be lucky to kill a tank in PVP or get him  dead to start.<P>Ok saying that I will tell you my story I am a 55 wiz on VZ<P>The Wiz was my first char I played and VZ is the only server I played on 1 to 25 was good I got owned a lot. But was still fun I gave as well as I got most times. <P>25 was hard playing in OT and WW but I learned a lot.<P> 26 to 47 was cake and had a good time<P> 48 sucked 49 to 53 was good killed lots of Sprocs  <P>54 OMG took forever<P>55 there is no place I can solo that gives good EXP and groups are hard to find. At 55 for the last 3 months the only groups you can find are from guys looking to get out of some place like deep Chardok, or Hs or Seb or PG lol<P> Pvp notes<P> I really hate it that a 53 Druid can kill me with one cast Winged death. I&#8217;m hit all I can do is gate and try to dispell before I die.  I am good with Pvp casters if I get the first cast in but still its one cast of tears and 2 droughts and if anything misses or resists I got to run or there pet will own me.<P>Pet notes <P>I was all happy when I first heard we as the Wiz class where getting pets my thought was finally something to even it up and to make soloing possible and look what we got a joke for a pet.<BR>Should have just told up it was a buff spell not a pet.<BR>. <BR>Loot note<BR>You got no cash tanks forget to split and they get all the loot you don&#8217;t dare say anything or forget getting into another group. At 55 I find that a mage or an Epic rouge can out damage me even if I chain cast.<P>To close this up I know lots of you are say goto td and kill the raptors to lvl.  I have tried. 2 to 3 druids there at any time and one cast I&#8217;m dead I got to use all my mana just to kill one.   By the time I&#8217;m meded up, there back to loot and WD me out of spite. <P>I have started an SK and a enchanter  I love the chanter it is so simple to pay speed clarity and AE mez and group is happy. Oh ya you just got to OOC call once with the enchanter LFG.<BR>With the Wiz you Can call for hours and still no group.<P>Well that&#8217;s where Im at thanks if you got this far lol <P>Mricon 55 Wiz VZ<BR>Dark Defiant Warrior<P>--------------------<P>Mricon 55 Wiz VZ <BR>Dark Defiant Warrior
